<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.american.edu/projects/mandala/TED/ural.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.american.edu/projects/mandala/TED/ural.htm" rel="nofollow">A report on the 1957 accident and on endemic radioactive pollution at Mayak.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.nti.org/db/nisprofs/russia/fissmat/pumayak/pomayak.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.nti.org/db/nisprofs/russia/fissmat/pumayak/pomayak.htm" rel="nofollow">Material prepared for the Nuclear Threat Initiative by the Monterey Institute's Center for Nonproliferation Studies.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.globalsecurity.org/wmd/world/russia/chelyabinsk-65_nuc.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.globalsecurity.org/wmd/world/russia/chelyabinsk-65_nuc.htm" rel="nofollow">Chelyabinsk-65 / Ozersk Combine 817 / Production Association Mayak. From GlobalSecurity.org.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.uralpress.ru/english/show_region.php?id=4" class="external text" title="http://www.uralpress.ru/english/show_region.php?id=4" rel="nofollow">On Ozersk and Mayak, from the Ural Press.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.thebulletin.org/issues/1999/so99/so99larin.html" class="external text" title="http://www.thebulletin.org/issues/1999/so99/so99larin.html" rel="nofollow">Eyewitness accounts of unsafe working conditions at Mayak.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://archive.greenpeace.org/mayak" class="external text" title="http://archive.greenpeace.org/mayak" rel="nofollow">Campaign to clean up Mayak. From Greenpeace web site.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://archive.greenpeace.org/mayak/mayakstory/index.html#Mayak%20Story" class="external text" title="http://archive.greenpeace.org/mayak/mayakstory/index.html#Mayak%20Story" rel="nofollow">More from Greenpeace</a></li>
<li><a href="http://context.themoscowtimes.com/stories/2002/05/24/107.html" class="external text" title="http://context.themoscowtimes.com/stories/2002/05/24/107.html" rel="nofollow">Article from the Russian press</a></li>
<li><a href="http://nuclear.tatar.mtss.ru" class="external text" title="http://nuclear.tatar.mtss.ru" rel="nofollow">URAL CHERNOBIL: TRAGEDY of TATARS</a></li>
<li><a href="http://nuclear.tatar.mtss.ru/arx-e1.htm" class="external text" title="http://nuclear.tatar.mtss.ru/arx-e1.htm" rel="nofollow">The book F.Bajramova "The nuclear archipelago or atomic genocide against Tatars" (1st chapter)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://alsos.wlu.edu/qsearch.aspx?browse=places/Mayak,+Russia" class="external text" title="http://alsos.wlu.edu/qsearch.aspx?browse=places/Mayak,+Russia" rel="nofollow">Annotated bibliography for the Mayak nuclear complex from the Alsos Digital Library for Nuclear Issues</a></li>
</ul>
